Millions of women across the U.S. are making their voice heard, supporting their legal right to abortion, this came after a recent draft opinion was leaked showing the Supreme Court may decide to overturn abortion rights. Once the U.S. Supreme Court delegates abortion law to states, experts say that may set the stage for a constitutional crisis. In this episode, CGTN walks you through the U.S.'s decades-old battle over abortion rights. And why this draft opinion has shocked America?